Subject: Ways to deal with stress
Atmosphere: Supportive
Abstract: Members share different ways to cope with stress
Opinion: 
A: Journaling is helpful
B: Relaxation techniques and taking breaks are beneficial
C: Physical activity and positive self-talk can reduce stress
D: Talking to someone and taking care of oneself can make a difference

